title: Elastic and inelastic scattering of 50-MeV alpha particles by 6Li and 7Li nuclei: The role of exchange in anomalous scattering at large angles

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Physics of Atomic Nuclei, Vol.59, p.29 (1996)

x4freetext: Russian original of J,PAN,59,29,1996
Metallic Li (100 to 500 ug/cm2) evaporated onto very
thin (~20 ug/cm2) organic films.
Thin Delta-E counter and ~1 mm thick E counter
at small angles (below 80 to 90 deg, detector
resolution of within 250 to 300 keV)
Single thin surface barrier detector at large
angles (above 80 to 90 deg, detector resolution of
within 350 to 400 keV)
